- Note that when instantiaing the adapter that the 4th parameter is a string array of the columns **From** which the data to be displayed is extracted and that the 5th parameter is an int array of the id&#39;s in the layout for each row that correspond to the 4th parameter.

- As such the SimpleCursorAdapter is quite flexible (more so or more simpler than SimpleAdapter) in regards to what can be displayed.


